CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 17, 1965, pg. 24 reads: "Gabfest - Diamond talk was the order of the day at Forbes Field, on Monday, prior to the beginning of the opening day game between the Pirates and the Giants..."
TitMainTitle: Man in Pittsburgh Pirates baseball uniform, possibly manager Harry Walker, wearing dark varsity style jacket, posed at dugout steps on Forbes Field for 1965 season opener
